<lb n="0004c14"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0004c15"/>
<lb n="0004c16"/>
<lb n="0004c17"/><head type="no">No. 1031</head>
<lb n="0004c18"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0004021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】天永三年寫東寺三密藏本</note>聖觀自在菩薩心真言瑜伽觀行
<lb n="0004c19"/><note n="0004022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">儀軌＝軌儀【三】</note><note n="0004022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">儀軌＝軌儀【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0004022"><lem>儀軌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">軌儀</rdg></app><note place="inline">出大毘盧遮那<note n="0004023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔成道〕－【甲】</note><app n="0004023"><lem>成道</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>經</note></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0004c20"/>
<lb n="0004c21"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0004024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔開府…智〕三十三字－【三】，（開府…智）三十三字＝（特進試鴻臚卿）六字【甲】</note><note n="0004024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔開府…智〕三十三字－【宋】【元】【明】，（開府…智）三十三字＝（特進試鴻臚卿）六字【甲】</note><app n="0004024" word-count="33"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0004c22"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0004c23"/>正號大廣智</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">特進試鴻臚卿</rdg></app><note n="0004025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大興善寺＝唐【明】</note><app n="0004025"><lem>大興善寺</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">唐</rdg></app>三藏沙<note n="0004026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">門＋（大廣智）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0004026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門＋（大廣智）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0004026"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0004c24"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0004c25"/><div1 type="jing"><p>夫修瑜伽者。先於靜處建立曼荼羅。以香水
<lb n="0004c26"/>散灑。以種種時華散<note n="0004027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔於〕－【甲】</note><app n="0004027"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>壇上。行者先須澡
<lb n="0004c27"/>浴著新淨衣。次入道場對尊像前。五輪投地
<lb n="0004c28"/>發殷重心。頂禮一切如來及諸菩薩。即結<note n="0004028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跏＝加【宋】【元】＊</note><app n="0004028"><lem>跏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">加</rdg></app>
<lb n="0004c29"/>趺坐。觀想諸佛如在目前。然後至誠懺一切
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1031.0005a" n="0005a"/>
<lb n="0005a01"/>罪。作如是言。我某甲自從無始已來。輪迴生
<lb n="0005a02"/>死乃至今日。所造眾罪無量無邊。不自覺知
<lb n="0005a03"/>自作教他見作隨喜。我今懺悔不復更造。<note n="0005001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】＊</note><note n="0005001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯＝惟【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0005001"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>
<lb n="0005a04"/>願諸佛慈悲攝受。令我罪障速得消滅<note place="inline">如是三說</note></p>
<lb n="0005a05"/><p>復應自誓受三歸依戒。作如是言。諸佛菩薩
<lb n="0005a06"/>哀愍<note n="0005002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">護＝授【甲】＊</note><app n="0005002"><lem>護</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">授</rdg></app>我。我某甲始從今日。乃至當坐菩提
<lb n="0005a07"/>道場。歸依如來無上三身。歸依方廣大乘法
<lb n="0005a08"/>藏。歸依僧伽諸菩薩眾<note place="inline">如是三說</note></p>
<lb n="0005a09"/><p>我某甲歸依佛竟歸依法竟歸依僧竟。從今
<lb n="0005a10"/>已往乃至成佛。更不歸餘二乘外道。<app type="＊" source="0005001"><lem>唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惟</rdg></app>願諸
<lb n="0005a11"/>佛慈悲攝受</p>
<lb n="0005a12"/><p>次<note n="0005003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔應〕－【甲】</note><app n="0005003"><lem>應</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>捨身供養。應作是言。諸佛菩薩願哀愍
<lb n="0005a13"/>故。攝受於我。從今已往乃至成佛。我常捨身
<lb n="0005a14"/>供養一切如來及諸菩薩。<app type="＊" source="0005001"><lem>唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惟</rdg></app>願慈悲哀愍加
<lb n="0005a15"/><app type="＊" source="0005002"><lem>護</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">授</rdg></app><note place="inline">如是三說</note></p>
<lb n="0005a16"/><p>次於最下方空中。觀賀字黑色。其字變成風
<lb n="0005a17"/>輪。其形半月。於風輪上。應觀&CB00085;字白色。其字
<lb n="0005a18"/>變成水輪其形圓滿。於水輪上。應觀囉字金
<lb n="0005a19"/>色。其字變成猛利金剛杵。流出金剛火焰其
<lb n="0005a20"/>形三角。從下向上至於地輪及以自身。火焰
<lb n="0005a21"/>焚燒唯有灰燼。即以此灰變成金剛輪。<note n="0005004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔其輪〕－【甲】</note><app n="0005004"><lem>其輪</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0005a22"/>白色堅密。隨量大小其形正方。次於金剛輪
<lb n="0005a23"/>上。觀想八葉大蓮華。具寶鬚&CB00610;。於蓮華臺上。
<lb n="0005a24"/>想娑<note place="inline"><note n="0005005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（聲）【明】＊</note><app n="0005005"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">上聲</rdg></app></note>字黃金色。其字具無量光明。變此娑
<lb n="0005a25"/>字成聖觀自在菩薩。結<app type="＊" source="0004028"><lem>跏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">加</rdg></app>趺坐身如金色。圓
<lb n="0005a26"/>光熾盛。身<note n="0005006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">披＝被&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0005006"><lem>披</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">被</rdg></app>輕縠繒綵衣著赤色裙。左手當
<lb n="0005a27"/>臍執未敷蓮華。右手當胸作開華葉勢。具頭
<lb n="0005a28"/>冠瓔珞。首戴無量壽佛住於定相。作是觀已。
<lb n="0005a29"/>即結三昧耶印</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1031.0005b" n="0005b"/>
<lb n="0005b01"/><p>以二手當心。密合掌並&CB00594;二大指。誦真言曰</p>
<lb n="0005b02"/><p type="dharani">那莫三滿多母馱<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">引</note>阿<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0005005"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>三<note place="inline"><note n="0005007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲）【明】＊</note><app n="0005007"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">去聲</rdg></app></note>銘底哩<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0005b03"/>合</note>三銘三<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0005007"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>麼<note place="inline"><note n="0005008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鼻＋（聲）【明】</note><app n="0005008"><lem>鼻</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">鼻聲</rdg></app></note>曳<note n="0005009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0005009"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT20p0005b03"/>引</note>賀<app type="＊" source="0005009"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0005b04"/><p>誦真言三遍。以印印五處加持。所謂額右肩
<lb n="0005b05"/>左肩心喉頂上散之。由結此印。即能速滿十
<lb n="0005b06"/>地行願十波羅蜜。能見一切如來地。能超過
<lb n="0005b07"/>法道界。所謂超過勝解地淨心地如來地<note place="inline">名超過法
<lb n="0005b08"/>道界</note></p>
<lb n="0005b09"/><p>次結法界生印</p>
<lb n="0005b10"/><p>以二手各作金剛拳側相著。&CB00594;二頭指頭側
<lb n="0005b11"/>相<note n="0005010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝跓【甲】＊</note><app n="0005010"><lem>拄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">跓</rdg></app>。置於頂上。即於頂上想&CB00772;字。從<note n="0005011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">字＝宇【宋】【元】</note><app n="0005011"><lem>字</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">宇</rdg></app>流
<lb n="0005b12"/>出白色光。遍照自身及以內外。即觀自身等
<lb n="0005b13"/>同法界。誦真言曰</p>
<lb n="0005b14"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0005012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那＝娜【明】</note><app n="0005012"><lem>那</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">娜</rdg></app>莫三<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0005007"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>滿多母馱<note place="inline">引</note>南<app type="＊" source="0005009"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>達<note n="0005013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">磨＝摩【三】</note><note n="0005013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">磨＝摩【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0005013"><lem>磨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>馱<app type="＊" source="0005009"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>都
<lb n="0005b15"/>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note n="0005014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引去＝去引【宋】【元】，去聲引【明】，〔引去〕－【甲】</note><note n="0005014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引去＝去引【宋】【元】，＝去聲引【明】，〔引去〕－【甲】</note><app n="0005014"><lem><note place="inline">引去</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">去引</note></rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">去聲引</note></rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00085;句<note place="inline">引</note>憾</p>
<lb n="0005b16"/><p>誦真言三遍。以印從頂上便分。二<note n="0005015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拳＋（從頂）【甲】</note><app n="0005015"><lem>拳</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">拳從頂</rdg></app>兩邊徐
<lb n="0005b17"/>徐下散</p>
<lb n="0005b18"/><p>次結轉法輪印</p>
<lb n="0005b19"/><p>以二手當心。背相附以右押左。四指互相鉤。
<lb n="0005b20"/><note n="0005016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">左＝右【甲】</note><app n="0005016"><lem>左</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">右</rdg></app>手大拇指。<note n="0005017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祕＝&CB03366;【甲】</note><app n="0005017"><lem>祕</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB03366;</rdg></app>於右手掌中。以<note n="0005018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">右＝左【甲】</note><app n="0005018"><lem>右</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">左</rdg></app>手大拇
<lb n="0005b21"/>指頭相<app type="＊" source="0005010"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">跓</rdg></app>。觀自身如金剛薩埵菩薩。左手執
<lb n="0005b22"/>金剛鈴置於左&CB03437;上。右手持五<note n="0005019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">股＝鈷【宋】</note><app n="0005019"><lem>股</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">鈷</rdg></app>杵當心作
<lb n="0005b23"/>跳躑勢。身如白月色頂戴五佛冠坐月輪中。
<lb n="0005b24"/>誦真言曰</p>
<lb n="0005b25"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0005020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娜＝那【甲】＊</note><app n="0005020"><lem>娜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">那</rdg></app>莫三<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0005007"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>滿多&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>喃<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合<note n="0005021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0005021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔引〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0005021"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0005b26"/>怛麼<note place="inline">二合</note>句<note place="inline">引</note>憾</p>
<lb n="0005b27"/><p>誦真言三遍已。即於頂上<note n="0005022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（當）＋散【甲】</note><app n="0005022"><lem>散</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">當散</rdg></app>印</p>
<lb n="0005b28"/><p>次結大日如來劍印</p>
<lb n="0005b29"/><p>以二手當心合掌。屈二頭指中節橫相<note n="0005023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跓＝拄【三】</note><note n="0005023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">跓＝拄【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0005023"><lem>跓</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">拄</rdg></app>。以
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1031.0005c" n="0005c"/>
<lb n="0005c01"/>二大拇指。並押二頭指上節如劍形。結此印
<lb n="0005c02"/>已。即觀自心中有八葉蓮華。於蓮華中想阿
<lb n="0005c03"/><note n="0005024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上〕－【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0005024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔上〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0005024"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>字。放金色光與印相應。想彼阿<app type="＊" source="0005024"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>字了
<lb n="0005c04"/>一切法本來不生。即誦真言曰</p>
<lb n="0005c05"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0005020"><lem>娜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">那</rdg></app>莫三<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0005007"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>滿多母馱<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">引</note>惡<note place="inline">引</note>尾<app type="＊" source="0005009"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>囉吽
<lb n="0005c06"/><app type="＊" source="0005009"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>欠</p>
<lb n="0005c07"/><p>誦真言八遍。以印如前加持自身五處。於頂
<lb n="0005c08"/>上散印</p>
<lb n="0005c09"/><p>次結普供養印</p>
<lb n="0005c10"/><p>以二手合掌。右押左交上節<note n="0005025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔即〕－【明】</note><app n="0005025"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>成。誦真言
<lb n="0005c11"/>曰</p>
<lb n="0005c12"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0005020"><lem>娜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">那</rdg></app>莫三<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0005007"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>滿多母馱<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0005026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">南＝喃引【甲】</note><app n="0005026"><lem>南</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">喃引</rdg></app>薩&CB00085;他<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0005007"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app>引</note>欠嗢
<lb n="0005c13"/>娜&CB00617;<note n="0005027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【三】</note><note n="0005027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔二合〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0005027"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>帝颯頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉呬<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00805;&CB00344;&CB00344;曩劍<note n="0005028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">平＋（聲）【明】，平＝引【甲】</note><app n="0005028"><lem><note place="inline">平</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">平聲</note></rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>
<lb n="0005c14"/>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT20p0005c09"/>引</note>賀<app type="＊" source="0005009"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0005c15"/><p>結印當心。誦真言五遍。想從印流出無量無
<lb n="0005c16"/>邊香華飲食。供養盡虛空遍法界一切賢聖。
<lb n="0005c17"/>於頂上散印</p>
<lb n="0005c18"/><p>次觀行布字法</p>
<lb n="0005c19"/><p>修瑜伽者應觀想。自身眉間置吽字。赤金色。
<lb n="0005c20"/>變成白<note n="0005029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毫＝豪【三】</note><note n="0005029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毫＝豪【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0005029"><lem>毫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">豪</rdg></app><note n="0005030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">相＋（先）【宋】【元】，（光）【明】</note><app n="0005030"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">相先</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">相光</rdg></app>。於腦交縫內置暗字。白色光
<lb n="0005c21"/><note n="0005031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滿＋（明）【甲】</note><app n="0005031"><lem>滿</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">滿明</rdg></app>其腦中。於頂上置&CB00772;<app type="＊" source="0005024"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>字。作赤色光分
<lb n="0005c22"/>焰上掣。於佛頂上應想唵字白色光照法界。
<lb n="0005c23"/>於自右足掌置娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>字。左足掌置賀字。即
<lb n="0005c24"/>觀自心為菩提心。離一切我離蘊處界能取
<lb n="0005c25"/>所取。於法平等。了知自心本來不生空無自
<lb n="0005c26"/>性。是故應當觀察。自心非我人眾生壽者等
<lb n="0005c27"/>性。何以故。彼我人等性。無所造作無所得故。
<lb n="0005c28"/>我人等本無。寧有自性。即得遠離一切我見。
<lb n="0005c29"/>是心亦非蘊處界性。何以故。此<note n="0005032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蘊＋（處界）【甲】</note><app n="0005032"><lem>蘊</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">蘊處界</rdg></app>等<note n="0005033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">性＝世【三】</note><note n="0005033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">性＝世【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0005033"><lem>性</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">世</rdg></app>。於
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1031.0006a" n="0006a"/>
<lb n="0006a01"/>勝義中實不可得故。蘊處界分別自性。即非
<lb n="0006a02"/>彼心。是心亦非能取所取。非彼能取妄想之
<lb n="0006a03"/>心。非彼所取青黃等相故。世尊言。心不住內
<lb n="0006a04"/>亦不住外不住中間。何以故。本來清淨無分
<lb n="0006a05"/>別故。如是觀察則知自心無我平等。了一切
<lb n="0006a06"/>法本來不生。離妄分別。皆無自性猶如虛空。
<lb n="0006a07"/>緣諸有情思惟愍念。<note n="0006001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彼＝從【甲】</note><app n="0006001"><lem>彼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">從</rdg></app>無始來不知自心本
<lb n="0006a08"/>來清淨。妄生分別顛倒鬼魅之所噉嚼。於生
<lb n="0006a09"/>死中受種種苦。我今云何起大精進。<note n="0006002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝於【明】</note><app n="0006002"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">於</rdg></app>諸
<lb n="0006a10"/>有情覺悟自心。了清淨法。令彼遠離虛妄分
<lb n="0006a11"/>別。如是大悲為菩提心。發是心已。於囉字上
<lb n="0006a12"/>具圓點。即為&CB00772;字為法界種子。想二囉字置
<lb n="0006a13"/>二眼中。如盛燈光普照一切。用此光明智慧
<lb n="0006a14"/>之眼。觀自心中所置阿<app type="＊" source="0005024"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>字。了一切法本來
<lb n="0006a15"/>不生。即於阿字流出白色光明。照無邊塵沙
<lb n="0006a16"/>世界。<note n="0006003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">除＝際【三】</note><note n="0006003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">除＝際【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0006003"><lem>除</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">際</rdg></app>一切有情身中無明癡闇。即想自身
<lb n="0006a17"/><note n="0006004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">轉成＝得成【宋】【元】，轉【甲】</note><note n="0006004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">轉成＝得成【宋】【元】，＝轉【甲】</note><app n="0006004"><lem>轉成</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">得成</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">轉</rdg></app><note n="0006005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔毘〕－【三】</note><note n="0006005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔毘〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0006005"><lem>毘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>盧遮那如來。具頭冠瓔珞坐白蓮
<lb n="0006a18"/>華。身如金色光明照曜<note n="0006006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（作）＋住【三】【甲】</note><note n="0006006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（作）＋住【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0006006"><lem>住</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">作住</rdg></app>三摩地。相應如是
<lb n="0006a19"/><note n="0006007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">觀＋（一切已）【三】</note><note n="0006007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">觀＋（一切已）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0006007"><lem>觀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">觀一切已</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0006a20"/><p>次結觀自在菩薩心印</p>
<lb n="0006a21"/><p>以二手內相叉。<note n="0006008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">翹＝剋【甲】</note><app n="0006008"><lem>翹</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">剋</rdg></app>&CB00594;<note n="0006009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝右【三】【甲】</note><note n="0006009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二＝右【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0006009"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">右</rdg></app>大拇指。印相即成。
<lb n="0006a22"/>結印當心。誦觀自在菩薩心真言七遍。以印
<lb n="0006a23"/>加持心額喉頂。<note n="0006010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔誦〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0006010"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0006a24"/><p type="dharani">唵阿<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0005007"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app>引</note>嚧<note place="inline">引</note>力迦<note place="inline"><note n="0006011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迦半音呼＝半音【甲】</note><app n="0006011"><lem>迦半音<note n="0006012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呼＋（方音中含迦字也下同）【明】</note><app n="0006012"><lem>呼</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">呼方音中含迦字也下同</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">半音</rdg></app></note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT20p0006a03"/>引</note>賀<note n="0006013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＝引去聲【宋】【元】，去聲引【明】</note><note n="0006013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引＝引去聲【宋】【元】，＝去聲引【明】</note><app n="0006013"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">引去聲</note></rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">去聲引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0006a25"/><p>隨誦真言。以右大拇指向身招之。即成召請
<lb n="0006a26"/>即觀本尊心上有圓滿寂靜月輪。於月輪中
<lb n="0006a27"/>右旋安布陀羅尼字。其字皆放白色光遍周
<lb n="0006a28"/>法界。其光<note n="0006014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">還＋（來）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0006014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">還＋（來）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0006014"><lem>還</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">還來</rdg></app>入行者頂。於修瑜伽者心月
<lb n="0006a29"/>輪中。准前右旋布列了了分明。其字復放光
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1031.0006b" n="0006b"/>
<lb n="0006b01"/>明。准前作觀。如是觀已。修瑜伽者自身與本
<lb n="0006b02"/>尊觀自在菩薩身。等無差別。如彼鏡像不一
<lb n="0006b03"/>不異</p>
<lb n="0006b04"/><p>次應思惟字義。阿<app type="＊" source="0005024"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>字門者一切法本不生
<lb n="0006b05"/>故。囉字門者一切法遠離塵故。&CB00256;字門者一
<lb n="0006b06"/>切法相不可得故。此&CB00256;字為加聲。變成力字。
<lb n="0006b07"/>從此力字中。流出迦<note n="0006015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">字＋（門）【甲】</note><app n="0006015"><lem>字</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">字門</rdg></app>。迦字門者一切法
<lb n="0006b08"/>無造作故。應如是觀繫心於真言文字之上。
<lb n="0006b09"/>即思字下所詮義門。謂本來不生等如上<note n="0006016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">四＝句&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0006016"><lem>四</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">句</rdg></app>
<lb n="0006b10"/>義如是作觀終而復始。名為三摩地念誦。若
<lb n="0006b11"/>作出聲<note n="0006017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念＋（誦）【甲】</note><app n="0006017"><lem>念</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">念誦</rdg></app>者。於真言中應<note n="0006018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">作＝加【甲】</note><app n="0006018"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">加</rdg></app>此句。<app type="＊" source="0006010"><lem>誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>真
<lb n="0006b12"/>言曰</p>
<lb n="0006b13"/><p type="dharani">唵阿<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0005007"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app>引</note>嚧<note place="inline">引</note>力迦<note n="0006019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔力者中含迦字也〕－【明】</note><app n="0006019"><lem><note place="inline">力<note n="0006020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＝音【宋】【元】【甲】</note><app n="0006020"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【甲】" resp="Taisho">音</rdg></app>中含迦字也</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>枳<note place="inline">引</note>囉底<note place="inline">二合丁<note n="0006021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">異反下同＝以切【明】</note><app n="0006021"><lem>異
<lb n="0006b14"/>反下同</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">以切</rdg></app></note><note n="0006022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02744;＝洛【明】【甲】</note><app n="0006022"><lem>&CB02744;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">洛</rdg></app>乞<note n="0006023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">灑＋（二合）細註【甲】</note><app n="0006023"><lem>灑</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">灑<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>弭<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0005007"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>尾步底銘娜娜娑&CB00085;<note place="inline"><note n="0006024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝三【三】</note><note n="0006024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二＝三【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0006024"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">三</rdg></app>合<anchor id="fxT20p0006b05"/>引</note>
<lb n="0006b15"/><note n="0006025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0006025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賀＋（引）細註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0006025"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0006b16"/><p>次應觀前阿<note n="0006026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚧力＝囉&CB00256;【三】，羅&CB00256;【甲】</note><note n="0006026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚧力＝囉&CB00256;【宋】【元】【明】，＝羅&CB00256;【甲】</note><app n="0006026"><lem>嚧力</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">囉&CB00256;</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">羅&CB00256;</rdg></app>迦等四字黃金色。誦前真
<lb n="0006b17"/>言即得增益。法中所求皆得。前所觀心中阿
<lb n="0006b18"/><app type="＊" source="0005024"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>字及腦中暗字。體是一也。眼中囉字頂上
<lb n="0006b19"/>&CB00772;字。如是四字義。以成自身等覺句也。復觀
<lb n="0006b20"/>菩提心。即結前三昧耶印。及結前法界生轉
<lb n="0006b21"/>法輪并劍印等。加持自身五處。各誦本真言。
<lb n="0006b22"/>即禮佛發願迴向已出道場。常轉大乘華嚴
<lb n="0006b23"/>般若等教。及印佛印塔經行。旋遶窣堵波令
<lb n="0006b24"/>速成就</p>
